```plantuml
@startuml gapfish_deployer

actor User

participant "depctl CLI" as CLI
participant "Kubernetes Cluster" as K8s
participant "Deployment Tool" as DeployTool
participant "Event Stream Logger" as Logger

User -> CLI: Trigger deployment
CLI -> DeployTool: Send deployment request
DeployTool -> K8s: Apply YAML configurations
K8s -> DeployTool: Acknowledge deployment
DeployTool -> Logger: Log deployment start
loop For each application component
    DeployTool -> K8s: Deploy component
    K8s -> DeployTool: Deployment status
    DeployTool -> Logger: Log component status
end
DeployTool -> K8s: Finalize deployment
K8s -> DeployTool: Deployment completed
DeployTool -> Logger: Log deployment completion
CLI -> User: Deployment status

@enduml
```